  "passage": [
    "Zed rides a small rocket-scooter on the moon. A friendly robot named Dot beeps and follows. They wear shiny helmets and carry a bag of letters. |“Moon Mail—let’s deliver!” says Zed.",
    "The path is bumpy with craters. Grey dust puffs up with each hop. Dot shines a light to show the way. |“Careful over the big crater,” beeps Dot.",
    "They stop at Base A. Zed stamps each letter with a star stamp. |“Post from Earth!” he says. The astronauts cheer and wave.",
    "One last letter slides out of the bag. It fell under a rock. Zed picks it up and smiles. |“Delivery complete,” he says. Dot spins and beeps with joy."
  ],
